        Chicago, Illinois, United States
      </p>
      As a AI Engineer for EY, I work on GenAI engagements which involve building LLM applications in python for clients. Such applications include RAG Chatbots, Structured Field Extraction, and LLM Agents. When I am not building GenAI apps, I do web scraping. 

      <!-- Engagement History for 2021 using details for a dropdown effect -->
       <details>
