          </li>
        </ul>
      </details>
       <details>
        <summary>2023 Engagements</summary>
        <ul>
          <li>
            For a client in Energy, I was the lead developer of a GenAI-powered solution that enabled structured data extraction from incoming emails that would be used as part of a automated RFP response pipline through Salesforce
          </li>
          <li>
            In between projects, I was a pioneer in GPT development with <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tommasobabucci/" target="_blank">@Tommaso Babucci</a>. As part of the GPT Core Team, I developed GenAI use cases for business teams. For an internal team, I helped developed a Retrive Augment Generate (RAG) Chatbot that answered questions about the SAP project delivery method. I helped with the inital scraping the internal wiki pages and loaded the pages into a Azure AI search index
          </li>
        </ul>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>2022 Engagements</summary>
        <ul>
          <li>
             For a client in banking, I worked with a EY team to connect financial metrics with employee experience metrics. As a follow up, I started scraping employee reviews from a variety of sources (glassdoor, blind, etc).
          </li>
